      <title>大银行面临掉期、清算业务保密协议调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/nda-probes-are-expanding-to-large-banks-swaps-clearing-businesses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家最高金融监管机构正在要求华尔街大型银行在其掉期和清算业务中签订保密协议，以观察它们是否压制潜在的举报人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/nda-probes-are-expanding-to-large-banks-swaps-clearing-businesses</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 15:56:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
